text: b'RT if you have an eating disorder'
b'I tried to commit suicide last night guys'
b"Don't ever stop believing in yourself"
b"@pumpkinarry you're a beautiful person and you inspire me daily."
b"@Helpisokay no need to lose weight darling, you're perfect as you are."
b"@help_stop_SH you CAN do this. Stay strong, you're perfect"
b"@NoLongerStrong you're in my prayers. You're beautiful :)"
b'How are all my little warriors?'
b"Do you ever feel like everyone hates you? Like, no matter what you do, you'll never be enough?"
b'Why is it raining here D:'
b'If you want to talk, just DM me.'
b"I have anxiety and depression.. I'm anorexic and I self harm.. But I'm proud of who I am."
b"Everyone has a story what's yours?"
b"@SayNoToSuicide4 You're beautiful and my inspiration"
b"If you're suffering from suicide, self harm, an eating disorder, anxiety, depression, or ANYTHING else.. I'm here for you."
b"The mirror can lie, doesn't show you what's inside."
b'There is a lot of pain in your scars, but more beauty in the person who created them.'
b"Whatever you're going through people, don't let it hold you down or let it govern the goodness in you. Stay Positive and Strong.\xe2\x99\xa1"
b'Love is louder than the pressure to be perfect.'
b'You are wonderfully and beautifully made.'
b'@ddlovato Demi if you see this, please follow me it would mean the world to me.'
